<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>School Website</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body class="school-website">

<header>
  <h1>My School Name</h1>
</header>

<section>
  <h2>About Us</h2>
  <p>Brief description of your school: history, location, vision, and mission.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Clubs & Activities</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Science Club</li>
    <li>Debate Club</li>
    <li>Drama Club</li>
    <li>Sports Team</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Gallery</h2>
  <p>Add images of school events here. Example: <code>&lt;img src="images/event1.jpg" alt="Event"&gt;</code></p>
</section>

<footer>
  Built for the CodeOnDigital Schools Hackathon
</footer>

</body>
</html>
